<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Flatpak Automatic Repository</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; background: #f4f6f8; }
        .container { background: white; padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        h1 { color: #2c3e50; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-top: 0; }
        h2 { color: #34495e; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
        h3 { color: #2178b1; margin-top: 1.0rem; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
        h4 { color: #2c3e50; margin-top: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 0.3rem; }
        h5 { color: #7f8c8d; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        a { color: #1377ba; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
        a:hover { text-decoration: underline; color: #2178b1; }
        .code-block { background: #282c34; color: #abb2bf; padding: 1.2rem; border-radius: 6px; overflow-x: auto; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; white-space: pre; }
        .card { border: 1px solid #eaeaea; padding: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; background: #fafafa; }
        ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; list-style-type: square; }
        li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        details { background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding: 0.8rem; }
        .rpm-list { max-height: 280px; overflow-y: auto; margin-top: 0.5rem; padding-right: 0.5rem; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0; }
        .rpm-list li { padding: 4px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }
        .rpm-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        summary { font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; color: #2178b1; user-select: none; outline: none; font-size: 1.1rem; }
        .badge-latest { background: #02893b; color: white; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.65em; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 8px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
        .badge-latest-sm { background: #177bbe; color: white; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.7em; margin-left: 6px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .packages-grid { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 2rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
        .package-col { flex: 1; min-width: 300px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 2rem; text-align: center; font-size: 0.85em; color: #6c797a; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 1rem; }
        .fingerprint { font-family: monospace; background: #eee; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            body { background: #121212; color: #e0e0e0; }
            .container { background: #1e1e1e; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
            h1 { color: #ffffff; border-bottom-color: #333; }
            h2 { color: #eeeeee; }
            h3 { color: #64b5f6; }
            h4 { color: #e0e0e0; border-bottom-color: #333; }
            a { color: #64b5f6; }
            a:hover { color: #90caf9; }
            .card { background: #252525; border-color: #333; }
            .code-block { background: #111; border: 1px solid #333; }
            details { background: #2a2a2a; border-color: #444; }
            summary { color: #90caf9; }
            .rpm-list li { border-bottom-color: #333; }
            .footer { color: #888; border-top-color: #333; }
            .fingerprint { background: #333; color: #64b5f6; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 700px) {
            body { padding: 0.5rem; margin: 0; }
            .container { padding: 1.2rem; }
            h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
            .code-block { padding: 0.8rem; font-size: 0.8em; }
            .package-col { min-width: 100%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; text-align: left;">
            <pre class="cli-banner" style="font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
<span style="color: #00FFFF;">  ___ _       _               _    </span>
<span style="color: #55AAFF;"> | __| |__ _ | |_ _ __  __ _ | |__ </span>
<span style="color: #AA55FF;"> | _|| / _` ||  _| '_ \/ _` || / / </span>
<span style="color: #FF00FF;"> |_| |_\__,_|\__| .__/\__,_||_\_\</span>
<span style="color: #FF00FF;">                |_|</span> AUTOMATIC
            </pre>
        </div>
        <p>Welcome to the official repository for <strong>Flatpak Automatic</strong>. This project provides a secure, configurable, and systemd-native automation wrapper for Flatpak updates with Snapper snapshot integration.</p>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>📦 Installation (RPM-based)</h2>
            <p>Add the repository and install the package on Fedora or compatible RPM-based systems:</p>
            <div class="code-block"># Add the repository configuration
sudo tee /etc/yum.repos.d/flatpak-automatic.repo &lt;&lt;'EOF'
[flatpak-automatic]
name=Flatpak Automatic - Stable
baseurl=https://{{ github_repo.split('/')[0] }}.github.io/{{ github_repo.split('/')[1] }}/rpms/latest/stable/
enabled=1
gpgcheck=1
gpgkey=https://{{ github_repo.split('/')[0] }}.github.io/{{ github_repo.split('/')[1] }}/gpg.key

[flatpak-automatic-testing]
name=Flatpak Automatic - Testing
baseurl=https://{{ github_repo.split('/')[0] }}.github.io/{{ github_repo.split('/')[1] }}/rpms/latest/testing/
enabled=0
gpgcheck=1
gpgkey=https://{{ github_repo.split('/')[0] }}.github.io/{{ github_repo.split('/')[1] }}/gpg.key
EOF

# Update the package metadata cache
sudo dnf makecache

# Install the flatpak-automatic package
sudo dnf install flatpak-automatic</div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>📦 Installation (Debian-based)</h2>
            <p>Add the repository and install the package on Ubuntu, Debian, or compatible systems:</p>
            <div class="code-block"># Download the GPG key and convert it to a format APT understands
curl -fsSL https://{{ github_repo.split('/')[0] }}.github.io/{{ github_repo.split('/')[1] }}/gpg.key | sudo gpg --dearmor -o /usr/share/keyrings/flatpak-automatic-archive-keyring.gpg

# Add the repository to your system's sources list
echo "deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/flatpak-automatic-archive-keyring.gpg] https://{{ github_repo.split('/')[0] }}.github.io/{{ github_repo.split('/')[1] }}/debs stable main" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/flatpak-automatic.list

# Update your local package index
sudo apt-get update

# Install the flatpak-automatic package
sudo apt-get install flatpak-automatic</div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>🗂️ Available Versions & Channels</h2>
            {% if versions %}
                {% for version in versions %}
                    <div class="version-group">
                        <h3>{{ version.name }} {% if version.is_first %}<span class="badge-latest">LATEST</span>{% endif %}</h3>

                        {% for channel in version.channels %}
                            <details {% if version.is_first %}open{% endif %}>
                                <summary>Channel: {{ channel.name | capitalize }}</summary>
                                <div class="packages-grid">
                                    <div class="package-col">
                                        <h4>RPM Packages</h4>
                                        <ul class="rpm-list">
                                        {% if channel.rpms %}
                                            {% for pkg in channel.rpms %}
                                                <li><a href="rpms/{{ version.name }}/{{ channel.name }}/{{ pkg }}">{{ pkg }}</a>
                                                {% if version.is_first and loop.first %} <span class="badge-latest-sm">latest patch</span>{% endif %}
                                                </li>
                                            {% endfor %}
                                        {% else %}
                                            <li><em>No RPMs available.</em></li>
                                        {% endif %}
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="package-col">
                                        <h4>Debian Packages</h4>
                                        <ul class="rpm-list">
                                        {% if channel.debs %}
                                            {% for pkg in channel.debs %}
                                                <li><a href="debs/pool/main/f/flatpak-automatic/{{ pkg }}">{{ pkg }}</a>
                                                {% if version.is_first and loop.first %} <span class="badge-latest-sm">latest patch</span>{% endif %}
                                                </li>
                                            {% endfor %}
                                        {% else %}
                                            <li><em>No DEBs available.</em></li>
                                        {% endif %}
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
                <p>No versions found.</p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>🔗 Resources</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="gpg.key">Download Repository GPG Key (gpg.key)</a></li>
                <li><strong>GPG Fingerprint:</strong> <span class="fingerprint">8D12 D614 9E1E 5E83 29DD E6FD 9B99 A03F 6577 BF59</span></li>
                <li><a href="https://github.com/{{ github_repo }}">GitHub Source Code &amp; Documentation</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://github.com/{{ github_repo }}/issues">Report an Issue</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Generated on <strong>{{ build_date }}</strong> | Commit: <a href="https://github.com/{{ github_repo }}/commit/{{ build_sha }}">{{ build_sha[:7] }}</a> | Run ID: {{ build_run_id }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
